**What it covers:**

- **Page purpose & user goals** — Settings should feel like a personal preferences dashboard, not a technical control panel
- **Current UX/UI problems** (12 identified) — single scroll page, no categorization, dual implementations, no unsaved changes warning, browser `confirm()`, separate data route, no search, mobile burden
- **Proposed layout** — Tabbed/sidebar layout with 8 sections: Profile, Goal, AI Tutor, Study Plan, Notifications, Appearance, Advanced, Data
