- **States** — Empty, loading, error for all sections (validation errors inline, connection test inline, export/import progress)
- **Mobile/responsive** — Horizontal scrollable tabs on mobile, sidebar on desktop, sticky save button, native pickers
- **AI Tutor integration** — Reciprocal relationship: test connection before use, tone selection, automation level, save feedback linking to AI Tutor
- **Accessibility** — Full ARIA roles, keyboard nav, focus management, color contrast, semantic labels
- **Data sources** — Maps every displayed field to its context/service source
- **Design notes** — Progressive disclosure, privacy-first, section color coding, global-first language default, deep config isolation
